ce-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/my-chemical-romance-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/my-chemical-romance-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/my-chemical-romance-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>周末，在他们的 Facebook 页面上出现了一系列奇怪的帖子后<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/my-chemical-romance">，“我的化学浪漫”</a>团聚的希望破灭了。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-listid="30"><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/track/my-chemical-romance-new-song-the-foundations-of-decay-3224859"><b>My Chemical Romance 的新歌“The Foundations of Decay”是一次激烈、无畏的回归</b></a></li></ul><p>鉴于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/gerard-way-sparks-fan-speculation-about-new-my-chemical-romance-music-cryptic-instagram-post-2814263">乐队经常利用社交媒体来调侃各种项目</a>，当他们在 Facebook 上更改个人资料图片时，一些粉丝认为他们已经准备好了公告。</p><p>当乐队继续发布一些奇怪的帖子时，人们的怀疑越来越多， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/have-my-chemical-romance-been-hacked-or-is-it-part-of-a-comeback-3778501">导致粉丝们质疑是否即将举行合法的重聚，或者他们是否遭到了黑客攻击</a>。</p><p>乐队 Facebook 账户上分享的一则新闻报道指出乡村歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/keith-urban">基思·厄本 (Keith Urban</a> ) 疑似罹患前列腺癌，而另一则新闻报道则对<a href="https://www.cnn.com/2024/07/14/politics/corey-comperatore-trump-shooting-victim/index.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">科里·康佩托雷 (Corey Comperatore</a> ) 的去世表示悲痛，科里·康佩托雷在前总统唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 遭遇暗杀未遂的集会上被杀。另一位声称美国电视节目主持人格雷格·古特菲尔德成功“超越”了<em>《深夜秀》的</em><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stephen-colbert">斯蒂芬·科尔伯特。</a> </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C97qFj6v4AJ/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc